0.2.4 (2023-07-25)
=====
- Properly init and free XvdInstance
- Auto-reconnect to Pulseausio server at connection lost (Fixes #1)
- Update copyright year and bug report address
- Add basic GitLab pipeline
- Fix autotools warnings
- build: Bump GLib minimum required to 2.26
- Fix compilation warnings
- automake: INCLUDES -> AM_CPPFLAGS
- autoconf: Some updates
- Add `.gitignore`
- Post release version bump

0.2.2
=====
- Support for the MicMute key (Christian Pointner)
- New Xfconf channel "xfce4-volumed-pulse"
  - property "icon-style" (to enable symbolic icons, requires xfce4-notifyd>=0.3.2)
  - property "volume-step-size" (used to be in channel xfce4-mixer)

0.2.1
=====
- Fix unresponsiveness after communicating with daemon (LP: #1347272, thanks Alistair)
- Update bug reporting URL to Xfce Bugzilla
- Bump autoconf, automake, and libtool versions

0.2.0
=====
- Initial port to Pulseaudio.

0.1.x
=====
- Uses GStreamer backend, cf. <http://git.xfce.org/apps/xfce4-volumed/log/> for a list of changes.
